sentences: Rajan Ishan ((Nepali: राजन ईशान)) (Born 29 September 1978) is a Nepali singer, composer and one of the most popular music arrangers in the Nepali Music Industry.
He lived in India in his teen days.
Rajan's debut song baash maa chhaina mero mann as "my heart is not in my control" became an instant classic hit in 1990s.
Rajan began his acting career with the film, "Karkash" in 2013.
He then acted in "Awaran" in 2014, "2 Rupaiyan" and "Rudrapriya" in 2017
